{
  "info": {
    "name": "PZ10 — NGINX Load Balancer",
    "description": "Все проверки ПЗ10 через Postman.\n\nПеременные коллекции: `lb_url` (http://localhost:8080), `auth_url` (http://localhost:8081), `token` (подставляется после Login).\n\nПорядок: поднять `deploy/lb` и **auth** на хосте → **0. Auth** → папка **1** (по очереди или Collection Runner) → для отказа реплики — в терминале `docker compose stop tasks_1`, затем папка **2** → `docker compose start tasks_1`.\n\nЛоги с `instance_id` снимаются только из терминала (`docker compose logs`), не из Postman.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    { "key": "lb_url", "value": "http://localhost:8080" },
    { "key": "auth_url", "value": "http://localhost:8081" },
    { "key": "token", "value": "" }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "0. Auth (локально, не через LB)",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Login — сохраняет token",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{auth_url}}/v1/auth/login",
              "host": ["{{auth_url}}"],
              "path": ["v1", "auth", "login"]
            },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"username\": \"student\",\n  \"password\": \"student\"\n}"
            }
          },
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "var j = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (j.access_token) pm.collectionVariables.set('token', j.access_token);",
                  "pm.test('200', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
                  "pm.test('access_token', () => pm.expect(j.access_token).to.be.a('string'));"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "1. Через балансировщик ({{lb_url}})",
      "description": "Отправляйте запросы по порядку или выделите папку и **Run collection** (Runner). Для скрина round-robin удобно показать результаты Runner по запросам Whoami 1/6 … 6/6.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Health",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{lb_url}}/health",
              "host": ["{{lb_url}}"],
              "path": ["health"]
            }
          },
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('200', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
                  "var h = pm.response.headers.get('X-Instance-ID');",
                  "pm.test('X-Instance-ID', () => pm.expect(h).to.match(/^tasks-[123]$/));",
                  "var j = pm.response.json();",
                  "pm.test('instance в JSON', () => pm.expect(j.instance).to.eql(h));",
                  "pm.test('status ok', () => pm.expect(j.status).to.eql('ok'));"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "Whoami 1/6",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{lb_url}}/whoami",
              "host": ["{{lb_url}}"],
              "path": ["whoami"]
            }
          },
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('200', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
                  "var id = pm.response.headers.get('X-Instance-ID');",
                  "pm.test('X-Instance-ID', () => pm.expect(id).to.match(/^tasks-[123]$/));",
                  "pm.test('JSON instance', () => pm.expect(pm.response.json().instance).to.eql(id));"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
