    {
      "name": "2. После stop tasks_1 (отказ реплики)",
      "description": "1) В терминале из папки `deploy/lb`: `docker compose stop tasks_1`.\n2) Запустите запросы **Whoami A–E** (Send или Runner) — в ответах **не должно** быть `X-Instance-ID: tasks-1`.\n3) Верните реплику: `docker compose start tasks_1`.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Whoami A (failover)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{lb_url}}/whoami",
              "host": ["{{lb_url}}"],
              "path": ["whoami"]
            }
          },
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('200', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
                  "var id = pm.response.headers.get('X-Instance-ID');",
                  "pm.test('не tasks-1', () => pm.expect(id).to.match(/^tasks-[23]$/));"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ]
        },
